profile:
DC Custom Excavation is a company that provides multiple services for clients looking to start their next project and want a reputable reliable contractor.

My goal is to customize your project until you are satisfied with a design or plan that suits your needs.

I can provide quality and professional work in a timely manner. 

DC Custom Excavation can start your project installing your culverts, demoing an existing driveway, digging trenches for hydro, water or gas, excavating for concrete footings and base preparation, grading property for topsoil.  

I also can help save your property from drainage issues by grading your land, installing weeper tiles , or doing some shoreline repairs.
project_minimum: 5 Hour Minimum and machine float charge
warranty_terms: Please contact me to specify as each project is unique in its own design.
